sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser as Web Client (React)
    participant API as Node API (MonitorServer)
    participant Wing as Wing Console (Hardware)

    Note over Browser, API: WebSocket Connection (Port 3001)
    Note over API, Wing: OSC over UDP (Port 2223)

    User->>Browser: Open App
    Browser->>API: WebSocket Connect
    API->>Browser: Initial State (JSON)
    
    User->>Browser: Adjust Volume
    Browser->>API: Send Command { type: 'SET_MAIN_VOLUME', value: 50 }
    API->>Wing: Send OSC /ch/40/fdr 0.5
    
    Wing-->>API: OSC Update (if changed externally)
    API->>Browser: Broadcast State Update
    Browser->>User: Update UI

    loop Keep Alive (Every 9s)
        API->>Wing: /xremote
        Wing-->>API: Current Values
    end
